				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes, 1 delay is equal to 1/10th of a second, assuming you are not hasted.  So a 20 delay weapon attempts to hit once every 2 seconds.  A 30 delay weapon attempts to hit once every 3 seconds.  If you are hasted, the delay time will drop accordingly.</span></td>
